# Firebase Admin / service-account credentials. NEVER commit these — they grant
# full FCM send rights for the project. Provide them to the server via the
# FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_BASE64 env var (preferred) or by mounting the file
# at a path referenced by GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS.
*firebase-adminsdk*.json
*service-account*.json
google-services-account*.json
